<%- include("partials/header") %>

<section class="hero">
  <span class="hero-badge">🌱 Budgeting that grows with you</span>
  <h1>Grow your money, <span class="grow">one branch at a time</span>.</h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">
    MoneyTree is a simple budgeting and financial planning app. Track every
    shilling, scan receipts, set monthly budgets, and watch your savings
    goals grow.
  </p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start for free</a>
    <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">I already have an account</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="feature-grid">
  <div class="card feature-card">
    <span class="feature-icon">📸</span>
    <h3>Scan receipts</h3>
    <p>Snap a photo — MoneyTree reads it, fills in the amount, and picks the category for you.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card feature-card">
    <span class="feature-icon">📊</span>
    <h3>Monthly budgets</h3>
    <p>Set a limit per category and see exactly how much month is left in your money.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card feature-card">
    <span class="feature-icon">⏰</span>
    <h3>Smart alerts</h3>
    <p>Get warned before you blow a budget — with the projected damage and what it means for your goals.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card feature-card">
    <span class="feature-icon">🎯</span>
    <h3>Savings goals</h3>
    <p>Plan for the big things — an emergency fund, a trip, a laptop — and grow toward them.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<h2 class="section-title">How it works</h2>
<p class="section-sub">Three steps to healthier money habits.</p>
<section class="steps-grid">
  <div class="card step-card">
    <span class="step-num">1</span>
    <h3>Record as you spend</h3>
    <p class="muted">Log expenses in seconds or just photograph the receipt — every shilling lands in the right category.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card step-card">
    <span class="step-num">2</span>
    <h3>Set your limits</h3>
    <p class="muted">Give each category a monthly budget. MoneyTree tracks your pace and warns you before you overshoot.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card step-card">
    <span class="step-num">3</span>
    <h3>Watch it grow</h3>
    <p class="muted">Insights, trends, and savings goals show your progress — and what your habits cost you per year.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
